						.project-element-description
							A social, economic, or environmental issue to be explored and better understood through travel. Highlighting critical global issues and the changemakers addressing them.
		.col-md-6.project-element
			.project-element-image{style: "background: url('#{asset_path("background/fixerboat.jpeg")}') bottom center no-repeat"}
				.project-element-overlay
					.project-element-header
						2. Local Fixer
					.project-element-hover
						.project-element-description
							A local guide who can make it all happen. The fixer handles ground logistics and accommodation, while providing important cultural and historical context.
		.col-md-12{style: "margin-top: -100px;"}
			.project-element-logo-container
				.project-element-logo{style: "background: url('#{asset_path("logos/headerlogoemail.png")}') center center no-repeat"}
		.col-md-6.project-element
			.project-element-image{style: "background: url('#{asset_path("background/ColombiaRafting.jpg")}') center center no-repeat"}
				.project-element-overlay
					.project-element-header
						3. Engagement
					.project-element-hover
						.project-element-description
